02:34.655 --> 02:36.757
FLACK:
Cleaning crew found him
about an hour ago.

02:36.790 --> 02:39.460
Principal's on
his way in now.

02:39.493 --> 02:40.861
What was he doing
here on a Saturday?

02:40.894 --> 02:41.862
The SATs were
this morning.

02:41.895 --> 02:45.266
Best guess, he was
studying late last night,

02:45.299 --> 02:46.767
someone locked up
without knowing he was here.

02:46.800 --> 02:50.304
Kid doesn't come home
and his parents don't report it?

02:50.338 --> 02:53.173
Who knows what
his home life was like?

02:58.312 --> 02:59.680
Blunt and sharp force trauma.

03:05.586 --> 03:07.621
Here's your murder weapon
right here.

03:09.022 --> 03:10.591
Whatever happened,
it's safe to say

03:10.624 --> 03:12.560
our perp didn't have
much of a plan.

03:14.027 --> 03:16.697
And our vic's was snuffed out.

